column5:
Record the OPD number of the patient who 
returns to the health facility for service or 
follow ups as per IMNCI recommendations.
Record the unique identification X-ray unit number, that keeps the patient individually identified.
Record any previous X-ray/ imaging report
Record the kind of examination (s) carried out
Record clinical impression (suspicion) of the referring clinician.
Record 'Y' if a patient received radiotherapy and 'N' if not
Record reason(s) for patient referral from or to another HF
Record the size of the film/recording plate used
Record the total amount or fee charged for the services received or amount waived or exempted.
Record the number on the receipt given to the patient from the cash office or invoice number
Record the name of the Requesting Clinician
